      <title>美国购房申请数量升至 2 月以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/us-home-purchase-applications-rise-to-highest-since-february</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于购房者抓住借贷成本小幅下降和市场上房屋选择增多的机会，美国住房抵押贷款申请指标飙升至 2 月份以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/us-home-purchase-applications-rise-to-highest-since-february</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
